# No emojis

Do not use emojis in this project.

This applies to:

- User-facing text (labels, buttons, toasts, errors, empty states).
- Comments and documentation.
- Commit messages and PR descriptions when working in this repo.

Use plain text instead. Icons from Nuxt UI or Lucide (`i-lucide-*`) are fine when an icon is needed in the UI.

## Example

```vue
<!-- AVOID: emoji in user-facing text -->
<template>
  <p>Subida completada 🎉</p>
</template>

<!-- CORRECT: plain text -->
<template>
  <p>Subida completada</p>
</template>
```

```typescript
// AVOID: emoji in comments
// Done! ✅

// CORRECT: plain text
// Upload finished successfully
```
